00:12:01.456 --> 00:12:06.103
az m'iz geven in shtub, durkh di fentster hot men gezen oyfn ander zayt

00:12:07.071 --> 00:12:09.630
az me firt mentshn.

00:12:10.227 --> 00:12:12.347
⟨oyfn⟩ di ander zayt hot men

00:12:12.387 --> 00:12:18.383
zikh tsugegreyt tsu a geto tsu makhn, ober mir hobn nit gevust az me geyt makhn, vos me geyt makhn, ven...

00:12:18.383 --> 00:12:20.531
mir hobn nit gevust, nor me hot

00:12:21.128 --> 00:12:24.176
genumen a gantse nakht aroysgefirt mentshn.

00:12:24.672 --> 00:12:31.905
ge- dan iz nokh mayn tate geven, ven m'hot di mentshn aroysgefirt. hot men gemakht far alemen azoy fun a tsikhl rukzaks

00:12:31.962 --> 00:12:32.833
un m'hot

00:12:32.856 --> 00:12:40.477
zakhn ongeton: vesh, a por zakhn, un a, a por harte broyt hot men gemakht, sukhares.

00:12:40.652 --> 00:12:44.746
un m'hot gezogt, tomer me vert farlorn, tomer me nemt undz ⟨un-⟩ tsu,

00:12:44.770 --> 00:12:47.244
zol yederer hobn epes

00:12:47.318 --> 00:12:48.577
tsum esn.

00:12:49.883 --> 00:12:51.463
hot men,

00:12:52.583 --> 00:12:53.353
ye.

00:12:53.494 --> 00:12:56.705
hot men ongegreyt pekelekh far yedern,

00:12:56.705 --> 00:12:57.633
ober

00:12:57.633 --> 00:13:00.913
