00:13:00.936 --> 00:13:06.110
nakher hot zikh aroysgevizn az di mentshn vos me hot genumen

00:13:06.471 --> 00:13:07.676
bay nakht,

00:13:07.770 --> 00:13:09.904
hot men zey aroysgefirt

00:13:10.048 --> 00:13:14.564
un m'hot zey alemen avekgefirt oyf Ponar un m'hot zey alemen geshosn.

00:13:14.588 --> 00:13:21.467
un dos hot men oysgeleydikt dortn a sakh geslekh. s'iz nit geven keyn groyse gasn; dortn iz shmole geslekh geven.

00:13:21.490 --> 00:13:23.526
un m'hot tsugegreyt far a geto.

00:13:24.156 --> 00:13:27.899
in, dervayle iz gekumen tsu loyfn bay undz oyfn hoyf

00:13:27.899 --> 00:13:29.010
a froy,

00:13:29.472 --> 00:13:31.373
vos zi, ir shviger

00:13:31.834 --> 00:13:33.887
hot gevoynt bay undz oyfn hoyf.

00:13:34.332 --> 00:13:36.385
iz zi gekumen tsu loyfn

00:13:36.475 --> 00:13:39.287
far tog, ven s'iz geven fintster,

00:13:39.664 --> 00:13:42.479
in a langn mantl, a nakete,

00:13:42.479 --> 00:13:44.349
mit a lokh in pleytse.

00:13:44.355 --> 00:13:46.812
zi iz geven fun di zelbe mentshn

00:13:46.819 --> 00:13:48.602
vos m'hot aroysgefirt

00:13:48.777 --> 00:13:50.188
fun di geslekh.

00:13:50.633 --> 00:13:58.760
un zi, mit a man un a yingele, a zun... mitn yingele fleg ikh zikh shpiln, vayl er fleg kumen tsu di boben...

00:13:59.307 --> 00:14:01.354
hobn zey alemen dershosn,

00:14:01.354 --> 00:14:06.472
un zi, zet oys az di koyl hot ir getrofn nor, ober nit derharget.

00:14:06.512 --> 00:14:09.676
hot zi zikh oyfgevekt in mitn nakht,

00:14:09.676 --> 00:14:16.074
iz zi gegangen tsu a goye, hot zi ir gegebn a mantl, un zi iz gekumen tsu loyfn tsu undz oyfn hoyf, tsu di bob-, tsu di shviger.

00:14:16.992 --> 00:14:24.320
un ⟨s'i- m'hot⟩ ale hobn moyre gehat tsu reydn afile, ober ale hobn gezen vos, un zi dertseylt vos iz forgekumen, az m'hot alemen oysgeshosn,

00:14:24.320 --> 00:14:25.136
ober

00:14:25.159 --> 00:14:27.397
di mentshn hobn, dos nit gekent

00:14:27.437 --> 00:14:31.313
farshteyn az aza zakh ken pasirn. m'hot do⟨kh sh-⟩ gezen;

00:14:31.313 --> 00:14:37.809
ikh aleyn ⟨ho-⟩ bin ikh oykh, vayl ikh bin arop dortn tsu mayn khaverte, iz, di, di, vu UNK dortn gevoynt oykhet.

00:14:38.642 --> 00:14:42.669
un s'hot genumen efsher tsvey teg, dray teg,

00:14:42.861 --> 00:14:43.912
hot men,

00:14:43.912 --> 00:14:47.344
oyf di gas vu m'hot zey alemen aroysgefirt, gehakt,

00:14:47.518 --> 00:14:49.350
bay di ende fun gas,

00:14:49.350 --> 00:14:55.629
azoy vi es geyt a gesl, bay di ende fun gas hot men gemakht azoy vi a groysn toyer, fun holts hot men geklapt.

00:14:56.007 --> 00:14:58.211
un in a tsvey teg arum,

00:14:58.217 --> 00:15:05.838
hot men undz genumen, iz aroys a bafel: ale zoln geyn in di geto. s'iz gevorn a geto, ale zoln geyn in di geto.

00:15:06.942 --> 00:15:13.804
iz, bin ikh geven un mayn muter un mayn shvester; mayn tate un mayn bruder iz shoyn nit geven. un mayn kleyner bruderl.

00:15:13.827 --> 00:15:21.010
un me hot genumen vos hot..., m'iz nit geven tsu vayt fun geto, hot men genumen in di hent vifl me hot gekent.

00:15:21.117 --> 00:15:25.313
un oyfn hoyf iz gegangen der strozh, der, der goy,

00:15:25.656 --> 00:15:28.370
un fun ale hayzer hot er ongeshlept

00:15:28.370 --> 00:15:33.766
vos... m'hot dokh gornit gekent nemen; m'hot genumen a por peklekh. hot er geshlept sh- kishns

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:37.285
un, zakhn, un koldres, un altsding,

00:15:37.285 --> 00:15:42.991
un er iz arayn in a voynung bay eyner vos iz dortn geven bay undz oyfn hoyf a raykher man,

00:15:42.991 --> 00:15:45.860
iz er arayn in zayn voynung, alts farnumen,

00:15:45.860 --> 00:15:49.612
un geshlept fun ale hayzer tsu zikh in shtub arayn.

00:15:49.737 --> 00:15:51.268
un undz ⟨ho-⟩

00:15:51.268 --> 00:15:52.869
zaynen mir gegangen in geto.

00:15:53.061 --> 00:16:02.741
m'iz arayn in geto, iz fun, fun umetum hobn zikh yidn geshlept mit peklekh, vifl m'hot gekent, un m'iz arayn in geto. m'iz arayn in geto...

00:16:03.338 --> 00:16:05.256
 iz men arayn in geto,

00:16:05.363 --> 00:16:09.289
iz geven a voynung vu a mol hot mayne a mume gevoynt. od-

00:16:09.413 --> 00:16:11.938
oder m'hot zey aroysgefirt ersht,

00:16:12.383 --> 00:16:15.004
 vos m'hot zey derharget. zaynen mir arayn

00:16:15.004 --> 00:16:16.393
in dem voynung.

00:16:16.467 --> 00:16:23.905
un nakher iz gekumen mayne tantes, un mayn, nokh tantes, un nokh tantes, un onkls, un ale zaynen mir arayn in dem voynung,

00:16:23.905 --> 00:16:26.214
un mir zaynen shoyn geven in geto.

00:16:27.233 --> 00:16:34.517
un nakher zaynen arayn andere mentshn. es iz geven in gantsn dray ROOMS. iz men dortn geven efsher draysik mentshn.

00:16:34.911 --> 00:16:36.023
ober m'hot,

00:16:36.023 --> 00:16:37.937
m'iz gelegn oyf der erd.

00:16:37.937 --> 00:16:40.051
un m'iz gehat, in geto,

00:16:40.210 --> 00:16:45.570
az m'iz arayn in geto hot men oykhet gehat ale tog andere gezetsn.

00:16:46.302 --> 00:16:48.827
ershtns hot men gedarft geyn tsu an arbet.

00:16:49.052 --> 00:16:52.336
der vos iz nit gegangen tsum arbet flegn zey arestirn.

00:16:52.967 --> 00:17:01.078
un THEN iz in di geto ho- hot men gehat shaynen. s'iz geven gele shaynen un PINK shaynen, un s'iz geven bloye shaynen.

00:17:01.253 --> 00:17:03.511
un, v-

00:17:03.511 --> 00:17:12.553
un s'iz geven ale vayle ⟨otshistkes⟩ in geto. vos heyst ⟨otshistkes⟩? me hot aroysgefirt fun geto ale vayle grupes mit mentshn,

00:17:12.795 --> 00:17:15.084
un m'hot avekgefirt oykh oyf Ponar.

00:17:15.765 --> 00:17:18.999
iz, di vos hobn gehat di gele shaynen

00:17:19.646 --> 00:17:20.838
zaynen,

00:17:21.012 --> 00:17:27.621
hobn gemegt lebn, heyst dos, vayle, dos iz geven vos zey hobn oysgeklibn. di andere flegn zikh darfn bahaltn.

00:17:27.645 --> 00:17:30.372
i- un mir hobn nit gehat keyn geln shayn,

00:17:30.396 --> 00:17:34.457
fleg ikh zikh bahaltn, mayn muter un mayn shvester un mayn bruderl.

00:17:34.665 --> 00:17:38.017
un m'iz geven SOMETIMES teg bahaltenerheyt:

00:17:38.327 --> 00:17:41.243
in a keler, oyf a boydem...

00:17:41.243 --> 00:17:43.821
un, nit ge⟨k-⟩...

00:17:42.748 --> 00:17:47.416
vos, vos iz dos ershte mol i- ir gedenkt, az m'hot zikh bahaltn

00:17:43.821 --> 00:17:44.700
ye.

00:17:47.457 --> 00:17:50.016
tsulib di saynen, di, tsulib di shaynen?

00:17:50.781 --> 00:17:57.055
m'hot zikh bahaltn, un zey flegn arumgeyn, di daytshn, un s'flegn kumen Ukrayner, s'flegn kumen alerle-...

00:17:55.995 --> 00:17:58.874
, vos iz dos ershte mol? kent ir dermonen?

00:17:58.797 --> 00:18:00.816
vos heyst, dos ershte mol?

00:18:00.518 --> 00:18:02.666
 dos ershte mol vos ir gedenkt,

00:18:02.666 --> 00:18:04.562
ven m'hot zikh bahaltn.

00:18:03.960 --> 00:18:07.143
eyn mol hob ikh zikh bahalt-, dem ersht- oyf a boydem.

00:18:07.403 --> 00:18:08.257
gelegn...

00:18:07.504 --> 00:18:09.568
un vos hot, vos, vos iz forgekumen?

00:18:09.343 --> 00:18:10.383
dos iz sh-

00:18:09.568 --> 00:18:11.643
vi azoy hot ir gevust az s'vet zayn

00:18:11.643 --> 00:18:14.230
an aktsye, az me muz zikh bahaltn?

00:18:12.415 --> 00:18:19.836
oh, vi azoy hot men gevust? me hot gezogt: az me geyt aroys ⟨vet⟩ men, me, az s'iz an aktsye. me,

00:18:19.806 --> 00:18:22.095
⟨ver?⟩ iz geven a klang oyf der gas?

00:18:19.836 --> 00:18:20.694
fun ⟨m-⟩...

00:18:21.443 --> 00:18:22.528
a klang.

00:18:22.528 --> 00:18:24.652
a klang. un s'iz azoy geven.

00:18:24.652 --> 00:18:30.667
ershtns iz azoy: s'iz geven dokh a yidisher, JUDENRAT. s'iz geven a firer a yidisher.

00:18:29.796 --> 00:18:31.275
ver hot ongefirt?

00:18:30.960 --> 00:18:32.855
 Gens. er iz geven...

00:18:32.855 --> 00:18:34.298
un s'iz gekumen,

00:18:34.298 --> 00:18:40.573
 WEISS, a y- a daytsh un s'iz geven MURER, un zey hobn farlangt azoy fil un azoy fil yidn.

00:18:40.883 --> 00:18:42.007
tsum...?

00:18:41.727 --> 00:18:43.031
ts- z-

00:18:43.031 --> 00:18:44.909
m'hot nit gezogt "tsum teytn."

00:18:45.895 --> 00:18:48.454
"tsu der ar-" m'hot nit gezogt "tsum teytn."

00:18:48.814 --> 00:18:50.481
me darf azoy...

00:18:49.303 --> 00:18:51.170
tsum aroysshikn?

00:18:50.481 --> 00:18:54.681
y- aroysshikn. m'hot nit gezo-, me, zey hobn dokh UNK ⟨, farleyknt, ye⟩.

00:18:54.687 --> 00:18:55.400
nu,

00:18:55.400 --> 00:18:57.397
hot men dokh gemuzt gebn zey,

00:18:57.792 --> 00:18:59.507
tsi er hot ye gevelt, tsi nit.

00:18:59.513 --> 00:19:04.551
iz, hot men azoy o, der vos hot nit gehat di shayn hot zikh bahaltn.

00:19:04.812 --> 00:19:09.078
der vos hot nit... vayle der shayn, der bloyer, der griner iz gornit vert geven;

00:19:09.078 --> 00:19:19.942
er iz geg- m'iz gegangen oyfn ban arbetn, azoyne andere arbetn vos iz tsu zey nit geven vikhtik. z- zey hobn ale mol gekent gefinen arbeter. nor di gele shaynen ⟨ho-⟩ zaynen geven mer SPECIAListn far zey.

00:19:20.387 --> 00:19:30.188
iz, hot men zikh bahaltn. hot men zikh bahaltn oyf a boydem, hot men zikh bahaltn in a keler, hot men zikh bahaltn, di mentshn vos hobn di shaynen, unter a bet bay zey a mol.

00:19:30.188 --> 00:19:31.637
zey hobn oykh moyre gehat.

00:19:31.710 --> 00:19:33.965
un me fleg zikh haltn in eyn bahaltn.

00:19:34.478 --> 00:19:37.782
nakher hot pasi- un, nakher...

00:19:36.233 --> 00:19:39.990
⟨u-⟩ un, ober ir hot ge- ikh hob gevolt, ir zolt bashraybn

00:19:40.300 --> 00:19:44.270
dos ershte mol ven ir hot zikh bahaltn: vu iz ⟨do⟩s, dos geven? UNK

00:19:43.810 --> 00:19:45.711
ikh bin aroyf a boydem.

00:19:45.126 --> 00:19:47.000
un vi hot oysgezen? UNK

00:19:46.493 --> 00:19:49.544
der boydem iz dokh a fintsterer, kleyner boydem.

00:19:49.544 --> 00:19:52.927
un m'iz gelegn azoy vi a moyz ligt in a lokh bagrobn.

00:19:52.927 --> 00:19:54.437
un me hot moyre gehat

00:19:54.437 --> 00:19:55.970
a hust tsu ton

00:19:56.162 --> 00:19:58.147
un, u- un a nis tsu ton.

00:19:58.288 --> 00:20:03.689
un tomer iz nokh aroyf mentshn mit a kind, hot men aroyfgeleygt a kishn, az ⟨der⟩ kind zol nit

00:20:03.689 --> 00:20:04.475
veynen.

00:20:04.937 --> 00:20:07.144
PLENTY kinder hobn mame-,

00:20:07.144 --> 00:20:11.849
ni- vayl mentshn hobn zikh bahaltn, un ⟨a⟩ kind vet veynen, hot men dokh bald, ye.

00:20:11.923 --> 00:20:14.426
nakher iz geven ⟨a⟩...

00:20:13.223 --> 00:20:17.807
iz, ven ir zayt geven dort dos ershte mol, ver iz geven mit aykh?

00:20:17.593 --> 00:20:26.919
ver iz geven? ⟨me,⟩ dem ershtn mol bin ikh geven mit mayn shvester, un s'iz geven dortn a por shkheynim vos hobn zikh bahaltn, ⟨iz men⟩ gelegn oyfn boydem, ye.

00:20:27.145 --> 00:20:29.261
ir hot gehert dem daytsh?

00:20:27.279 --> 00:20:28.290
⟨u-⟩

00:20:28.680 --> 00:20:34.001
me hot gehert az me geyt, un me redt, un me hot,

00:20:34.001 --> 00:20:40.082
ge-, SURE, hot men gehert. s'iz der boydem; der boydem iz dokh a hiltserner boydem vos iz geven, ye.

00:20:40.392 --> 00:20:47.169
un nakher iz geven eyn mol ven m'hot aroysgefi-..., bahaltn zikh hob ikh efsher zeks, zibn mol.

00:20:47.192 --> 00:20:51.256
eyn mol bin ikh arayn in a TOILET. bin ikh geven mit mayn,

00:20:51.256 --> 00:20:52.294
C- a COUSIN,

00:20:52.294 --> 00:20:56.484
a yingele efsher fun zibn yor, mayn tante's, yingele.

00:20:56.254 --> 00:20:59.970
dos heyst in a tsimer a klozet? ⟨vu⟩ iz geven, ⟨a⟩ TOILET?

00:20:58.397 --> 00:21:00.922
NO, a kl⟨a-⟩ a, a, a TOILET.

00:21:01.300 --> 00:21:03.203
⟨d-⟩ arayn in a TOILET, ⟨m'hot⟩...?

00:21:02.380 --> 00:21:08.955
a TOILET, nor s'iz geven n- n- ⟨es⟩ iz geven tsu shteyn oyf di fis, aza, ir't azoy ⟨o⟩ geshtanen, ye.

00:21:08.117 --> 00:21:09.220
ah.

00:21:08.995 --> 00:21:11.469
a TOILET. bin ikh arayngelofn mit im.

00:21:11.728 --> 00:21:16.075
un m'hot farma- un mir hobn farmakht di tir. un in TOILET iz dokh geven vi a TOILET.

00:21:16.167 --> 00:21:20.599
un ikh hob nor moyre gehat az er zol nit veynen, a kind fun zibn yor.

00:21:20.723 --> 00:21:28.043
un do zaynen gekumen di Litviner tsi di, tsi, tsi di daytshn;, s'iz geven alerley NATIONS, ⟨⟩, militer vos iz gekumen.

00:21:28.043 --> 00:21:30.760
un zey hobn gehakt in tir un gehakt in tir.

00:21:30.760 --> 00:21:35.263
un ikh hob gehert vi zey zogn oyf litvish, "⟨NIEKO NĖRA⟩." dos heyst "keyner ⟨iz⟩ nito."

00:21:35.522 --> 00:21:36.494
mir hobn

00:21:36.552 --> 00:21:39.077
nit gekent BREATHEn afile!

00:21:39.235 --> 00:21:40.550
un ⟨zey⟩ zaynen avek.

00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:42.422
⟨zey⟩ zaynen avek, iz men aroys.

00:21:42.422 --> 00:21:49.206
s'hot genumen a bisl biz zey hobn oysgeklibn di mentshn, avekgefirt, dortn tsum, geto, tsum ende toyer,

00:21:49.206 --> 00:21:55.659
un nakher avekgefirt zey tsu, ober zey marshirt ts-, tsu, tsu di Lukishker turme, un nakher hot men zey avekgefirt nokh

00:21:55.659 --> 00:21:57.735
AUSCH-, nokh,

00:21:57.735 --> 00:21:58.744
Ponar.

00:21:59.350 --> 00:22:00.441
un

00:22:00.480 --> 00:22:03.056
nakher hot genumen a tsveyt⟨er⟩ mol,

00:22:03.113 --> 00:22:04.426
hot men genumen,

00:22:04.426 --> 00:22:07.089
oyf dray teg hot men aroysgeshikt

00:22:07.332 --> 00:22:10.330
di mentshn vos hobn gehat di shaynen,

00:22:10.369 --> 00:22:11.409
di gele.

00:22:11.702 --> 00:22:17.400
hot men zey aroysgeshikt fun geto, do vu zey hobn gearbet. zaynen zey aroys oyf dray teg.

00:22:17.558 --> 00:22:22.187
un di ale vos zaynen geblibn iz geven ley-, di geto

00:22:22.187 --> 00:22:25.719
hobn di daytshn mit di u- Litviner, di Ukrayner

00:22:26.012 --> 00:22:30.916
gegangen oysreynikn di ale mentshn avektsufirn tsum toyt.

00:22:31.092 --> 00:22:38.176
mir zaynen aroyf oyf an ander boydem, un m'hot farbundn di boydem, dem dekhel-, di tirele mit shtrik, shtark,

00:22:38.176 --> 00:22:39.829
un m'iz gelegn, efsher,

00:22:39.829 --> 00:22:45.935
efsher fuftsn man? ikh ken nit zogn ⟨EX-⟩, genoy, ober s'iz geven a groys, a sakh mentshn. un m'iz gelegn.

00:22:45.739 --> 00:22:47.505
ver iz geven tsvishn aykh?

00:22:47.106 --> 00:22:50.930
s'iz geven mayn shvester, mayn muter, mayn bruderl.

00:22:50.953 --> 00:22:53.512
s'iz geven mayne tsvey onkls.

00:22:53.755 --> 00:22:55.757
un nakher fremde mentshn.

00:22:55.830 --> 00:23:01.781
un dan, in der tsayt iz shoyn geven, der, der bruder un der tate zaynen mer nishto?

00:23:00.167 --> 00:23:07.231
⟨,⟩ dos iz es. zey zaynen in geto shoyn nit arayn. zey zaynen shoyn nit arayn. zey zaynen geven fun di ershte. mayn tate fun di ershte gekhapt,

00:23:03.943 --> 00:23:04.909
⟨z-⟩

00:23:07.356 --> 00:23:12.260
un mayn bruder hot men farbrent fun di ershte. zey zaynen shoyn nit geven. nor ikh mit, ye.

00:23:11.136 --> 00:23:13.610
iz ale di, di lebedike nonte

00:23:13.465 --> 00:23:22.807
ye. un, oykh nit ale, ober s'iz nokh geven mayn onkl, mayn, di tante, di, mir zaynen geven bahaltn. di tante vos iz in Sinsineti iz oykh geven bahaltn.

00:23:13.802 --> 00:23:15.129
zaynen geven?

00:23:24.535 --> 00:23:27.265
mir zaynen geven oyfn boydem dray teg,

00:23:27.265 --> 00:23:30.421
iz men geven, vayl s'hot forgekumen dray teg,

00:23:30.421 --> 00:23:31.444
un, un...

00:23:31.444 --> 00:23:35.497
iz men gelegn farfrorene, hungerike dray teg oyfn boydem.

00:23:35.841 --> 00:23:39.007
mit eyn mol hot men gefunen undzer boydem

00:23:40.009 --> 00:23:41.251
un me hot...

00:23:41.848 --> 00:23:49.115
s'iz geven a vant vos iz arayn in yidishn shpitol, un m'hot aroysgenumen a por tsigl arayntsugeyn oyfn ander boydem.

00:23:49.290 --> 00:23:51.278
iz gekumen di daytshn

00:23:51.278 --> 00:24:02.374
mit, di Litviner, un zey hobn derzen di tsigl, un zey hobn aroysgenumen di tsigl, un zey hobn arayngerukt di kop, un zey hobn gezen undz oyfn boydem. hot men genumen raysn di tirl

00:24:02.374 --> 00:24:04.390
vos m'hot farbundn mit di shtrik,

00:24:04.390 --> 00:24:07.455
un m'hot genumen shpringen, ver s'hot ge- erloybt.

00:24:07.455 --> 00:24:09.213
ikh bin aropgeshprungen,

00:24:09.253 --> 00:24:12.605
un mayn muter, un mayn bruderl hot tsebrokhn a fus.

00:24:13.084 --> 00:24:15.947
un, mayn shvester

00:24:16.695 --> 00:24:25.042
hot shoyn nit aropgeshprungen ⟨shoyn⟩. vayle m'hot shoyn, ale hobn dokh nit gekent aropshpringen, un zey hobn gekhapt far di hent un nit gelozn shpringen,

00:24:25.403 --> 00:24:26.479
un

00:24:26.479 --> 00:24:28.876
dan hot men mayn shvester tsugenumen

00:24:29.031 --> 00:24:33.395
fun geto un m'hot ir avekgefirt nokh Ponar. ikh bin aropgeshprungen,

00:24:33.503 --> 00:24:34.509
iz,

00:24:34.515 --> 00:24:43.385
oyfn hoyf zaynen geven Litviner un, un di daytshn, un m'hot undz geheysn geyn, heyst es, aroysgeyn oyfn gas. oyfn gas hot men oyfgeklibn di partyes.

00:24:43.459 --> 00:24:44.865
ober oyfn gas,

00:24:44.865 --> 00:24:48.009
azoy vi er hot zikh gegebn a drey, bin ikh arayngelofn

00:24:48.792 --> 00:24:50.012
in a shtub,

00:24:50.012 --> 00:24:51.475
in a BASEMENT,

00:24:51.475 --> 00:24:58.759
un m'hot zikh vayter... mayn muter iz oykh aropgeshprungen epes vu in a BASEMENT, un mayn bruderl hot men genumen in shpitol vayl er hot tsebrokhn a fus fun shpringen.

00:24:59.406 --> 00:25:01.553
un mayn shvester hot men dan tsugenumen.

00:25:01.718 --> 00:25:03.096
hot men tsugenumen.

00:25:03.102 --> 00:25:07.821
nakher hot men ge- az zey hobn avekgefirt di partye, d- mentshn, di ⟨p-⟩

00:25:07.821 --> 00:25:12.210
tsum, hoyf, fun hoyf tsu di geto, bayn ende geto,

00:25:12.210 --> 00:25:15.493
hot men gemeynt az s'i- zey zaynen shoyn nito, s'iz shtil.

00:25:15.493 --> 00:25:19.611
bin ikh aroysgekrokhn fun, unter, dortn, vu ikh hob zikh bahaltn.

00:25:19.611 --> 00:25:23.155
dervayl⟨e⟩ zaynen zey tsurikgekumen. zey hobn yene avekgefirt, zaynen vayter gekumen.

00:25:23.155 --> 00:25:29.387
bin ikh tsurik aroyfgelofn oyfn boydem. zog ikh, "der boydem iz shoyn ofn; oyfn boydem hobn zey shoyn tsugenumen di mentshn.

00:25:29.545 --> 00:25:33.895
⟨zey veln⟩ shoyn nit krikhn." ⟨b-⟩ bin ikh shoyn gelegn dortn nokh a bisl,

00:25:33.895 --> 00:25:37.312
biz s'iz ariber di dray teg, s'iz gevorn shtil

00:25:37.312 --> 00:25:42.974
un di andere vos zaynen geven aroysgefirt fun geto zaynen gekumen tsurik in geto.

00:25:42.974 --> 00:25:46.531
iz dan hot men tsugenumen mayn shvester un s'iz vayter geven,

00:25:46.622 --> 00:25:51.088
 vayter gegangen der get-, der lebn, azoy vi es geyt in geto.

00:25:50.757 --> 00:25:56.319
iz, dan iz, ayer shvester, ⟨iz dos l-⟩ letste mol ir hot gezen ayer shvester?

00:25:55.515 --> 00:25:59.458
dos iz geven, ven ikh bin geven mit ir oyfn boydem. dan hot men ir tsugenumen.

00:25:59.160 --> 00:26:03.862
un dos briderl iz, iz, hot gelebt vayter tsulib dem vos er hot tsebrokhn dos fus?

00:25:59.574 --> 00:26:00.275
ye.

00:26:00.375 --> 00:26:01.688
der bruderl

00:26:01.688 --> 00:26:04.904
hot gelebt, ye. er iz aroys fun shpitol, ye,

00:26:04.904 --> 00:26:08.671
un er hot gelebt. un nakher bin ikh geven mit mayn mamen un mayn bruderl,

00:26:09.235 --> 00:26:11.794
 biz eyn sheynem tog,

00:26:12.475 --> 00:26:16.049
un ⟨a-⟩ un eyn tog b-, hob ikh nit gekent geyn tsu der arbet.

00:26:16.049 --> 00:26:20.934
ikh ⟨bin gega-⟩ ikh hob gearbet oyfn ban. ikh hob epes gehat hits; kh'hob nit gekent geyn tsu der arbet.

00:26:20.934 --> 00:26:23.994
hot men mir arestirt; az m'iz nit aroys tsu der arbet...

00:26:24.051 --> 00:26:26.593
un s'iz geven aza tfise in geto.

00:26:26.717 --> 00:26:32.594
un az, s'iz gevorn, az m'iz gekumen nokh mentshn take aroysfirn, hot ⟨men⟩ bald aroysgefirt

00:26:32.594 --> 00:26:33.663
fun tfise.

00:26:33.990 --> 00:26:36.481
bin ikh eyner dortn geven in tfise.

00:26:36.623 --> 00:26:40.112
es zet oys az zey hobn dan nit gekumen aroysfirn keyn yidn.

00:26:40.112 --> 00:26:44.396
hob ikh gehat mazl az ikh bin nit gevorn aroysgefirt, az ikh leb nokh.

00:26:44.807 --> 00:26:48.692
un in eyn sheynem tog, mir geyen avek tsu an arbet.

00:26:48.692 --> 00:26:54.622
mir flegn geyn ale in der fri, flegt men geyn oyfn ban arbetn, un oyfn ban hot men gearbet azoy vi mener.

00:26:54.662 --> 00:26:56.563
me hot geLOADet

00:26:56.569 --> 00:27:01.507
koyln un, shteyn-koyln un zamd un, me hot geleygt

00:27:01.598 --> 00:27:02.891
oyfn ban

00:27:02.914 --> 00:27:12.763
di relsn mit di holts, di grobe. mit negl flegt men klapn, azoy vi mener! oder me flegt makhn ⟨UNK⟩⟨koptsyes⟩, griber flegt men, kopenen.

00:27:13.410 --> 00:27:17.555
un mir zaynen gegangen tsu der arbet, mir zaynen gekumen tsu der arbet,

00:27:18.810 --> 00:27:19.718
un

00:27:19.718 --> 00:27:21.082
di daytshn

00:27:21.156 --> 00:27:26.955
shteyen... di daytshn, dos iz geven arbeter daytshn, nit, di S.S. dos iz geven azoy O.T.

00:27:27.180 --> 00:27:29.834
zey zaynen ale farputst mit rukzek,

00:27:29.834 --> 00:27:35.814
un zey fregn tsu undz, tsi mir zaynen, ⟨rayze fi-⟩, tsi mir zaynen READY tsu forn.

00:27:36.360 --> 00:27:39.234
hobn zikh ale arumgekukt: vos iz do geshen?

00:27:39.234 --> 00:27:44.539
hot men farshtanen az me firt undz tsum toyt, vayle zey hobn dokh ⟨y-⟩ ale mol azoy gezogt: "tsu der arbet."

00:27:44.967 --> 00:27:46.952
hobn mir ale genumen loyfn.

00:27:47.008 --> 00:27:50.832
un m'hot genumen loyfn; ale zaynen tselofn fun dem ban.

00:27:51.109 --> 00:27:55.164
un oyfn gas hot men dokh nit getort geyn, vayl m'hot dokh gehat lates;

00:27:55.164 --> 00:27:56.891
m'hot dokh getrogn lates.

00:27:57.184 --> 00:27:59.017
iz,

00:27:59.017 --> 00:28:09.682
hobn zikh oyfgeklibn, oyfgeklibn etlekhe meydlekh vos mir zaynen tselofn, un m'hot gemakht azoy vi tsen mentshn; m'iz gegangen azoy vi me geyt tsu an arbet, un m'iz gekumen tsurik tsum geto.

00:28:09.840 --> 00:28:14.778
me hot gemeynt, m'iz gekumen tsum geto, az mir zaynen shoyn antlofn fun toyt.

00:28:14.802 --> 00:28:20.938
m'iz gekumen tsum geto, zaynen geshtanen daytshn, un s'iz geshtanen a groyser oyto.

00:28:21.670 --> 00:28:26.676
un undz hot men shoyn in geto nit arayngelozn. m'hot undz far di geto dortn

00:28:26.682 --> 00:28:28.420
gehaltn in a,

00:28:28.420 --> 00:28:30.484
in a gesheft a leydikn,

00:28:30.484 --> 00:28:36.311
un biz s'zaynen gekumen nokh meydlekh un nokh meydlekh vos zaynen tselofn, un m'hot undz aroyfgevorfn

00:28:36.317 --> 00:28:37.731
oyfn oyto,

00:28:37.731 --> 00:28:39.956
un m'hot undz avekgefirt tsum ban.

00:28:40.047 --> 00:28:44.861
un m'hot undz avekgefirt tsum ban, m'iz gekumen tsum ban, iz dortn geshtanen vagonen

00:28:44.861 --> 00:28:47.730
vos me firt, ferd, di...

00:28:47.730 --> 00:28:54.505
un m'hot undz alemen arayngevorfn in di vagonen. in eyn vagon iz efsher geven fuftsik m- mentshn,

00:28:54.505 --> 00:28:56.032
froyen un mener,

00:28:56.032 --> 00:28:57.860
un fun nokh pletser:

00:28:57.867 --> 00:29:01.230
fun, AEROPORT, vos mentshn hobn gearbet,

00:29:01.230 --> 00:29:03.243
hot men zey oykhet gebrakht.

00:29:03.739 --> 00:29:07.715
un me hot zey alemen in di vagonen arayngev-

00:29:07.715 --> 00:29:11.394
-zetst, arayngevorfn. nit gezetst; m'hot undz arayngevorfn.

00:29:12.227 --> 00:29:14.583
un m'hot farmakht di vagonen

00:29:14.927 --> 00:29:16.996
un m'iz geforn.

00:29:17.273 --> 00:29:23.482
mir hobn nit gevust vu me fort un ven me fort, nor vos iz geven der gedank? az me fort nor tsum toyt.

00:29:24.411 --> 00:29:27.982
lomir vayter geyn nokhn, nokh dem vi me bayt iber di tashme.

00:29:28.478 --> 00:29:29.166
oh.
